Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:50.12,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}敬启  写给自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:53.69,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}如旧怀抱着的那份痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:57.27,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}是否是否会散去呢
